high_descs: Turn left and walk across the room, then hang a right and walk up to the counter to the left of the sink.
Open the leftmost cabinet door below the counter and take out the salt shaker.
Turn around and walk towards the wall, then turn right and walk over to the white table.
Put the salt shaker on the table to the left of the bottle of lotion.
Turn right and walk over to the black shelving unit, then look up at the upper cabinets.
Open the left upper cabinet door in front of you and take out the salt shaker that is inside, then close the cabinet.
Turn around and walk forward, then turn right to face the white table.
Put the salt shaker on the table to the left of the salt shaker that is already there.
anns.task_desc: Move two salt shakers to a white table.

high_descs: Turn left, turn right, face the counter to the left of the sink.
Open the cabinet door below the counter, pick up the salt shaker, and close the door.
Turn and walk to the counter on the right.
Put the salt shaker down to the left of the bottle.
Turn right and look up at the cabinet.
Open the cabinet door, take the salt shaker out of the cabinet, close the cabinet door.
Turn left and face the right side of the table.
Place the salt shaker on the table to the left of the first salt shaker.
anns.task_desc: To move two salt shakers to the white table.

high_descs: turn left and walk straight towards the table then turn right and walk straight towards the sink
open the cabinet door and remove the salt shaker and close the door
turn around and walk straight then turn right and walk straight towards the table
put the salt shaker down on the table next to the spray bottle
turn right and then look up at the cabinet
open the cabinet door and remove the salt shaker then close the door
turn around then walk straight then turn right at the white table
put down the salt shaker to the left of the other salt shaker
anns.task_desc: Clean up salt shakers and put them on to the table
